#'
#' - `Septic`
#'
#' Septic polynomial, fitted using 8 sample points.
#'
#' - `Quintic`.
#'
#' Quintic polynomial, fitted using 6 sample points.
#'
#' - `Cubic`.
#'
#' Cubic polynomial, fitted using 4 sample points.
#'
#' - `Linear`.
#'
#' Linear polynomial, fitted using 2 sample points.
#'
#' - `Nearest`.
